  "Description": {
    "English": "A collection of salvaged components from a Sentinel Hardframe, reconditioned to fit the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Minotaur</span> Heavy Exocraft Hybrid.<br><br>Installation will significantly improve the Minotaur's <span class=\"name name-technology\">engine and mobility</span> systems.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从一台护卫强化外壳上回收的构件，针对<span class=\"name name-technology\">弥诺陶洛斯</span>重型混合强化艇进行了改装处理。<br><br>安装后能够显著提升弥诺陶洛斯的<span class=\"name name-technology\">驱动器以及机动</span>系统。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從巡警硬體結構中回收的一系列元件，經過翻新後用於<span class=\"name name-technology\">彌諾陶洛斯</span>重型混合強化艇。<br><br>安裝後會顯著提升<span class=\"name name-technology\">引擎和機動性</span>系統。"
  },
